 be the players locations and 
\begin_inset Formula $d=dist(p1,p2)$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Formula $dist$
\end_inset

 is defined by the shortest path between 
\begin_inset Formula $p1$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $p2$
\end_inset

 on the circle perimiter.
 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 be the facility location.
 The 
