\emph default
 is defined as 
\begin_inset Formula $dist(p1,d)+dist(p2,d)$
\end_inset

.
 Define the circle perimiter length as 1 for convinience, notice every solution
 value is at most 1.
 The optimal solution for the problem is choosing the longest arc between
